name: Cosmic Valhalla Maiden Passive T3
passiveSkills: Grants +50% increase to all stats in battle
Reduce the healing of all enemies by 50%
Grant Immunity to Stop and all Stun effects, including Perfect and Innate Stuns, to all allies
Inflict Punish and Accuracy Down on a random enemy for 2 turns every action
This Talisman's effects only activates when equipped to a Valhalla Maiden character.
